{
  "stem": "9701.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there were some ladies on the platform who gave us cookies and juice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I still remember this, how good those cookies were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At 6 o'clock that evening, we boarded the ship in Hook Van Holland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's H-O-O-K, new word V-A-N, new word H-O-L-L-A-N-D.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the boat was not to leave until midnight and arrive in Harwich, H-A-R-W-I-C-H, England the following morning at 6 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't really remember much about boarding the ship or who I-- I know I shared [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the room, or whatever, the cabin, with someone.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I have no idea anymore who that was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] What I do remember is I, at some point, needed to go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I had learned that bathroom in English was water closet, or WC, and so I looked.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I walked around the ship, and it was a small ship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I walked around, looking for either water closet or WC, and I couldn't find it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then I decided, well, I'm just going to look on one side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, when I come the other, when I come back, I'll look on the other side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe I missed it and I did not see it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I asked one of the personnel from the boat, where is the water closet?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, there is none.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, where is the WC?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There is none.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I began to panic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't need to go to the bathroom urgently at that point, but until 6 o'clock tomorrow morning, before we get to England, I don't think I can make it.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
